WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love In A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.287
=Episode 1=

00:01:08.875 --> 00:01:09.795
(I)

00:01:10.050 --> 00:01:11.550
(fell for my elder brother.)

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.775
(We're not related by blood,)

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:18.050
(yet we're bound by countless ties.)

00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:21.160
(Living under the same roof,)

00:01:21.960 --> 00:01:24.337
(we conceal our feelings
for each other.)

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:27.360
(I ran toward him again and again,)

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:30.680
(yet he pushed me away
time and time again.)

00:01:33.012 --> 00:01:34.772
(But I remember)

00:01:34.875 --> 00:01:36.915
(that he was the one
who stirred my heart first.)

00:02:00.587 --> 00:02:04.025
(A Few Months Ago)

00:02:12.487 --> 00:02:14.237
(Lu Jiaming)

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:17.320
(Holding a wedding
on my mom's death anniversary?)

00:02:17.375 --> 00:02:19.335
(I wonder what their intentions are.)

00:02:22.650 --> 00:02:25.062
(Lu Jiaming)

00:02:49.040 --> 00:02:49.880
Sorry about that.

00:02:49.880 --> 00:02:51.237
I was distracted just now.

00:02:51.240 --> 00:02:52.690
That's why
I bumped into you by accident.

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:54.280
Do you have time today?

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:56.240
Should we go and fix your car together?

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:57.800
Or should we wait for
the insurance company to come?

00:02:58.680 --> 00:02:59.520
I'm not free today.

00:02:59.920 --> 00:03:00.960
I'm very busy.

00:03:01.060 --> 00:03:02.690
Why don't you give me
your contact, then?

00:03:02.962 --> 00:03:03.962
We can keep in touch.

00:03:09.837 --> 00:03:11.550
(Lu Zhu, 17889)

00:03:39.920 --> 00:03:40.920
Man?

00:03:41.500 --> 00:03:42.700
You guys should head out first.

00:03:45.700 --> 00:03:46.560
Why didn't you tell me

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:47.720
that you were back?

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:50.800
Mom,

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:52.400
congratulations on your wedding.

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:57.280
This looks great.

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:02.000
Let me take a look at you.

00:04:04.425 --> 00:04:05.225
I'm so glad

00:04:05.225 --> 00:04:06.180
that you're here today.

00:04:07.560 --> 00:04:09.280
However, the guests of our wedding today

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:11.440
mostly comprised of
Mr. Lu's business partners

00:04:11.440 --> 00:04:12.680
and relatives.

00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:14.320
Perhaps this isn't the time to...

00:04:14.320 --> 00:04:16.000
Mom, that's fine.

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:19.680
I'll introduce you to them

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:20.975
once the wedding is over.

00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:21.920
Okay.

00:04:24.300 --> 00:04:26.500
You weren't implicated by
your father's matter, right?

00:04:27.080 --> 00:04:28.240
I wasn't implicated.

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:30.520
But it was quite sudden.

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:32.160
There are still many
outstanding debt issues.

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:33.840
That's why I came back to resolve it.

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:35.360
But your father's matter

00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:36.400
was pretty bizarre.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.240
I know he went bankrupt,

00:04:38.480 --> 00:04:39.960
but why would he take his own life?

00:04:40.200 --> 00:04:42.790
Could it be that he actually
scammed people out of a lot of money,

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:44.680
just like what the rumors suggested?

00:04:45.160 --> 00:04:45.880
That...

00:04:47.480 --> 00:04:48.200
That can't be.

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:50.520
My dad will never scam anyone.

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:53.200
Ms. Huang.

00:04:53.200 --> 00:04:54.200
Are you ready?

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:55.390
We need to head to the scene now.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:55.880
Alright.

00:04:56.200 --> 00:04:56.720
I'm done.

00:04:57.840 --> 00:04:58.760
Dear guests,

00:04:58.760 --> 00:04:59.760
let's welcome

00:04:59.760 --> 00:05:01.680
the most unique officiant ever.

00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:03.320
Let's welcome Mr. Lu's daughter,

00:05:03.320 --> 00:05:04.680
Ms. Lu Zhu,

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:06.080
to give a speech.

00:05:28.600 --> 00:05:30.560
(So she's indeed Lu Jiaming's daughter.)

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:31.600
(I was right.)

00:05:32.760 --> 00:05:33.800
(What is he doing here?)

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:40.440
There are two things
worth sharing today.

00:05:41.440 --> 00:05:45.120
Firstly, my father

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:48.160
found his true love once again
at the age of 40.

00:05:49.240 --> 00:05:50.720
He needs my blessings.

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:56.280
Secondly, my mother, Shen Qi,

00:05:56.280 --> 00:05:58.980
she's still waiting for me to pay
my respects to her at the cemetery.

00:05:59.280 --> 00:06:01.040
Perhaps many of you have forgotten.

00:06:02.680 --> 00:06:05.080
Today's my mother's
second death anniversary.

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:09.520
Life is but a dream.

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:12.520
It doesn't matter who's the lead
or who's the supporting cast.

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:16.560
So Dad,

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:19.200
I'll definitely attend your wedding.

00:06:19.200 --> 00:06:21.480
However, I won't

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:22.880
give you my blessings.

00:06:30.175 --> 00:06:32.775
Congratulations on
being his official wife.

00:06:34.700 --> 00:06:36.020
You guys should head out first.

00:06:43.300 --> 00:06:45.400
You guys are so adept
at choosing your wedding date.

00:06:46.620 --> 00:06:49.530
Of all the dates, you just had to
do it during my mom's death anniversary.

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:52.400
Are you trying to tell the world

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:55.160
that Lu Jiaming has already
forgotten about his wife

00:06:55.900 --> 00:06:57.500
and that you're his only beloved?

00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:58.780
Lu, you misunderstood us.

00:06:59.150 --> 00:07:01.840
We chose the date because it was
a good date for the lunar calendar.

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:02.760
We forgot

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:04.880
about the Gregorian Calendar.

00:07:04.880 --> 00:07:06.760
I know you have a good memory.

00:07:07.320 --> 00:07:09.762
But you actually forgot about
your friend's death anniversary.

00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:12.000
Ms. Huang, you're so forgetful.

00:07:16.400 --> 00:07:17.800
As beautiful as you are,

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:21.080
you've passed your prime.

00:07:32.500 --> 00:07:33.990
(Today's my mom's death anniversary.)

00:07:34.180 --> 00:07:35.640
(Although I shouldn't force everyone)

00:07:35.640 --> 00:07:37.120
(to pay their respects to her,)

00:07:38.320 --> 00:07:43.200
(someone is actually celebrating
the very day. How ironic.)

00:07:43.200 --> 00:07:45.560
(I can only stage a silent protest)

00:07:45.560 --> 00:07:46.560
(using my own way.)

00:07:47.612 --> 00:07:50.372
(To protect that the deceased
was already replaced)

00:07:50.800 --> 00:07:52.460
(just after two years of passing.)

00:07:52.780 --> 00:07:54.687
(To protest that those who remember
her have to weep in silence)

00:07:54.687 --> 00:07:56.200
(while the newlyweds smile about it.)

00:07:56.680 --> 00:07:57.520
(To protest)

00:07:58.575 --> 00:08:01.360
(that all men are unfaithful.)

00:08:03.862 --> 00:08:06.079
(Once the ridiculous wedding is over,)

00:08:06.937 --> 00:08:08.864
(I'll become all alone again.)

00:08:09.800 --> 00:08:12.050
(I'll turn into the precious princess
of the Lu family,)

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:14.040
(whom no one cares about,)

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:16.840
(and has no one to depend on.)

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:19.200
We meet again.

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:25.895
So you were attending
my father's wedding too?

00:08:52.275 --> 00:08:53.623
Every tear you shed now

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:55.760
will flood the Milky Way

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:58.640
as they shine a light
on the path to home

00:08:58.640 --> 00:08:59.860
for the souls of the deceased.

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:02.880
Light will shine brightly on their path.

00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:05.040
Each star

00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:07.920
represents a part of their memories.

00:09:08.920 --> 00:09:10.100
If they're always remembered,

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:12.600
they won't vanish.

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:14.680
That's for you.

00:09:15.437 --> 00:09:16.560
What a lousy story.

00:09:17.262 --> 00:09:18.880
All stories that can cheer a kid up

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:20.840
are good stories.

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:22.000
What about you?

00:09:22.750 --> 00:09:24.590
Did the kin you longed for

00:09:24.760 --> 00:09:26.040
come to visit you?

00:09:26.900 --> 00:09:29.380
The intersection
we rear-ended each other

00:09:29.437 --> 00:09:31.237
was the only path down
from the cemetery.

00:09:32.025 --> 00:09:33.625
Who did you pay your respects to?

00:09:35.275 --> 00:09:36.075
My father.

00:09:42.520 --> 00:09:44.080
I think someone's calling for me.

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:46.320
I'll make a move first.

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:47.800
Thank you for your fairy tale.

00:09:55.325 --> 00:09:57.125
Man has returned.

00:09:57.130 --> 00:09:58.627
I already made a reservation
at a restaurant.

00:09:58.627 --> 00:09:59.987
Let's go see him.

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:04.570
At the age of 17, Xiao Man was admitted

00:10:04.580 --> 00:10:06.160
to Tsinghua University's Youth Program.

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.840
Now, he's starting
his own business in Shanghai.

00:10:35.687 --> 00:10:40.187
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:10:40.412 --> 00:10:44.200
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:10:44.375 --> 00:10:48.450
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:10:48.450 --> 00:10:52.587
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:10:52.712 --> 00:10:56.487
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:10:56.487 --> 00:11:00.262
♪I'll learn to stop
longing for what's gone♪

00:11:00.262 --> 00:11:02.537
♪The you in my memories♪

00:11:02.537 --> 00:11:04.550
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:11:04.550 --> 00:11:09.987
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:11:11.550 --> 00:11:16.987
♪Forget you completely♪